value: Resident, intra-African migrant and Palearctic winter visitor, wooded savannas with sparse ground cover: resident C Morocco - W Libya, Canary Is (epops); resident Nile Valley (major); resident and intra-African migrant all S part of Sahara and south except forest area and driest parts of NE and SW (africana, waibeli and senegalensis); Palearctic winter visitor Senegal - Eritrea (epops); all Madagascar except E (marginata).
